<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>{{title}}</title>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" type="text/css">
</head>
<body>
	<div id="background">
		<div id="page">
			{{> header}}  {{!-- Include header partial --}}

			<div id="contents">
				{{{body}}}  {{!-- Inject page-specific content here --}}
			</div>

			{{> footer}}  {{!-- Include footer partial --}}
		</div>
	</div>
</body>
</html>
Explanation:

{{title}}: Placeholder for dynamic page titles.
{{> header}}: Includes the header section from header.hbs.
{{{body}}}: Placeholder where the specific page content (like travel.hbs) will be injected.
{{> footer}}: Includes the footer section from footer.hbs.
